                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "There's no gas hookup. Climate control comes from 44 geothermal boreholes in a closed-loop system beneath the building. Rainwater is captured and reused. Solar panels cover the parking lot.",
